xaloon components

1. Requirements to compile
 You need to download and install these jars:
 <dependency>
			<groupId>javax.media</groupId>
			<artifactId>jai-core</artifactId>
			<version>1.1.3</version>
			<scope>provided</scope> 
		</dependency>
		<dependency>
			<groupId>com.sun.media</groupId>
			<artifactId>jai-codec</artifactId>
			<version>1.1.3</version>
			<scope>provided</scope>
		</dependency>
	Or add external repository to your settings.xml:
	<profiles>
		<profile>
			<id>xaloon-external-repositories</id>
			<activation>
				<activeByDefault>true</activeByDefault>				
			</activation>
			<repositories>
				<repository>
					<id>jboss-repository</id>
					<url>http://repository.jboss.org/nexus/content/groups/public-jboss/</url>
				</repository>
			</repositories>
		</profile>
	</profiles>	
	
2.